  "text": "Due to its high complexity of the search and widely adoption as the critical data path function in IP packet forwarding, packet classification is often a performance bottleneck in network infrastructure and it has received much attention in the research community. Besides the Decision Tree based algorithms [CITATION_1] [5-8] we mentioned in the previous sections, several other kinds of algorithms or hardware schemes are proposed, recently.",
